Package: skeletor
Type: Package
Title: Another R Package Skeleton Generator
Description: A tool for bootstrapping new packages with useful defaults, a test
    suite outline that passes checks, and helpers for pushing your package to
    'GitHub', adding documentation, and running tests, both locally and on
    hosted services.
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2016-12-21
Authors@R: c(person("Neal", "Richardson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "neal.p.richardson@gmail.com"))
Author: Neal Richardson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Neal Richardson <neal.p.richardson@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/nealrichardson/skeletor
BugReports: https://github.com/nealrichardson/skeletor/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
